        Returns:
        PromisedReply to be resolved or rejected when the connection is completed.

      • reconnectNow

        public void reconnectNow(boolean interactive,
                         boolean reset,
                         boolean background)
        Make sure connection is either already established or being established: - If connection is already established do nothing - If connection does not exist, create - If not connected and waiting for backoff timer, wake it up.
        Parameters:
        interactive - set to true if user directly requested a reconnect.
        reset - if true drop connection and reconnect; happens when cluster is reconfigured.
